channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: 25,000 ordered to evacuate as wildfires burn in Canada's Jasper National Park
item.description: At least 25,000 people have been forced to evacuate due to wildfires in Jasper National Park in Canada, officials said.

item.title: California single mom had no idea she owed tens of thousands of dollars in zombie mortgage debt
item.description: Teresa modified her home mortgage back in 2009 during the financial crisis, and thought she was making payments on her second mortgage every month. She's discovered she's overdue on thousands of payments for this "zombie debt," and fears losing her home.

item.title: Passenger plane crashes during takeoff in Nepal, killing 18
item.description: More than a dozen people were killed when a plane crashed during takeoff in Nepal on Wednesday, aviation officials said.

item.title: Renewables overproduction turns electricity prices negative
item.description: Read more on this topic here

item.title: California probation officer says zombie mortgage led to foreclosure
item.description: Jose Arzate of Santa Maria, California, says he was taken by surprise when sheriff's deputies evicted him. He says he never knew he owed tens of thousands of dollars in "zombie mortgage" debt.

item.title: The prosecutor vs. the felon. Democrats see winning contrast between Harris and Trump
item.description: Vice President Kamala Harris is leaning on her prosecutorial background as she gears up to take on Donald Trump, and Democrats see it as a winning message.

item.title: Iraq War veteran says she could lose her home because of a zombie mortgage
item.description: Laverne Simmons of Inglewood, California, says she never got bills for a decade-old debt. Now this "zombie mortgage" could cost her the home she loves.

item.title: Biden to give prime-time address on decision to exit 2024 race and what comes next
item.description: Biden will speak extensively for the first time on his decision to withdraw from the 2024 race and his plans for what will now be the final few months of his career.

item.title: Idaho murders suspect's lawyer wants trial moved to Boise
item.description: Brian Kohberger is charged with fatally stabbing students Kaylee Goncalves, Madison Mogen, Xana Kernodle and Ethan Chapin on Nov. 13, 2022.

item.title: High school coach, 28, randomly shot and killed at bar while attending conference
item.description: A 28-year-old high school coach was “randomly shot and killed” standing on a rooftop bar while she was in town for a conference, police said.
